{"tid":1569391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"囯旗保你一生平安，一人一枝中国国旗！！","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:18:32.000Z","uid":266808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8bf930ed6d96c91056305b14c7e1dba8091bc9","tid":1569391,"uid":266808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"拎住支紅旗<br />\n做乜都得<br />\n下次打廢老時拎住啲旗打柒班廢老<br />\n到時班狗來再屈鳩班廢老係黃絲<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗"},{"pid":"52b830c6f7051ee6e6cd3fdffba539de898770e2","tid":1569391,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75579210e081b2aba98706dd15f764adf9a31a15","tid":1569391,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=200f579d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"3e86b7cdc426c1cd9c934e178e67a58cc0fecc14","tid":1569391,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc8bf930ed6d96c91056305b14c7e1dba8091bc9","tid":1569391,"uid":266808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"拎住支紅旗<br />\n做乜都得<br />\n下次打廢老時拎住啲旗打柒班廢老<br />\n到時班狗來再屈鳩班廢老係黃絲<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"人地用支旗就叫愛國，我地用叫辱旗㗎喇~"},{"pid":"ab71b7a0974922eff03067dbe2d4de72334e6650","tid":1569391,"uid":114351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"Sign ➡️ email confirmation ➡️ signed ✅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">831恐襲 (30/9)</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=cdda1994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whi